data.name: UnratedDescription
data.value: Not rated yet.

data.name: GemMintDescription
data.value: The highest grade assigned. The collectible must have no evidence of any manufacturing or handling defects.

data.name: MintDescription
data.value: The collectible is nearly indistinguishable from a 10.0 but will have a very minor manufacturing defect. It will not have any evidence of handling defects.

data.name: NearMintMintDescription
data.value: A nearly perfect collectible with negligible handling or manufacturing defects.

data.name: NearMintPlusDescription
data.value: A very well-preserved collectible with several minor manufacturing or handling defects.

data.name: NearMintDescription
data.value: A very well-preserved collectible with minor wear and small manufacturing or handling defects.

data.name: NearMintMinusDescription
data.value: A very well-preserved collectible with some wear and small manufacturing or handling defects.

data.name: VeryFineNearMintDescription
data.value: A very well-preserved collectible with good eye appeal. There will be a number of minor handling and/or manufacturing defects.

data.name: VeryFinePlusDescription
data.value: An attractive collectible with a moderate defect or a number of small defects.

data.name: VeryFineDescription
data.value: An attractive collectible with a moderate defect or an accumulation of small defects.

data.name: VeryFineMinusDescription
data.value: An above-average collectible with a moderate defect or an accumulation of small defects.

data.name: FineVeryFineDescription
data.value: An above-average collectible with a major defect or an accumulation of small defects.

data.name: FinePlusDescription
data.value: An above-average collectible with a major defect and some smaller defects, or a significant accumulation of small defects.

data.name: FineDescription
data.value: A slightly above-average collectible with a major defect and some smaller defects, or a significant accumulation of small defects.

data.name: FineMinusDescription
data.value: A slightly above-average collectible with several moderate defects.

data.name: VeryGoodFineDescription
data.value: An average collectible with several moderate defects.

data.name: VeryGoodPlusDescription
data.value: A slightly below-average collectible with multiple moderate defects.

data.name: VeryGoodDescription
data.value: A below-average collectible with multiple moderate defects.

data.name: VeryGoodMinusDescription
data.value: A below-average collectible with several major defects or an accumulation of multiple moderate defects.

data.name: GoodVeryGoodDescription
data.value: A collectible that shows significant evidence of handling with several moderate-to-major defects.

data.name: GoodPlusDescription
data.value: A collectible that shows extensive evidence of handling with multiple moderate-to-major defects.

data.name: GoodDescription
data.value: A collectible that shows extensive evidence of handling with numerous moderate-to-major defects.

data.name: GoodMinusDescription
data.value: A collectible that shows extensive evidence of handling with numerous major defects.

data.name: FairGoodDescription
data.value: A collectible that shows extensive evidence of handling with a heavy accumulation of major defects.

data.name: FairDescription
data.value: A very poorly handled collectible with a heavy accumulation of major defects.

data.name: PoorDescription
data.value: A heavily defaced collectible with a number major defects. Some pieces will also be missing.
